[Naih] See,

788
00:40:39,702 --> 00:40:41,105
you've gone viral!

789
00:40:41,938 --> 00:40:45,342
See for yourself!
That's what you're doing!

790
00:40:46,010 --> 00:40:48,579
And you're laughing?!
Hold this, Migz!

791
00:40:49,146 --> 00:40:50,280
-[Naih] Really?!
-[Lorde] Not my Master!

792
00:40:50,414 --> 00:40:51,282
What?!

793
00:40:51,414 --> 00:40:53,050
Naih, stop!
Calm down and listen to me!

794
00:40:53,184 --> 00:40:55,552
I don't wanna listen
to your excuses!

795
00:40:55,686 --> 00:40:57,487
Stop fighting and listen to me!

796
00:41:01,192 --> 00:41:03,360
Ysay, show it to her please.

797
00:41:07,764 --> 00:41:08,632
What's that?

798
00:41:14,838 --> 00:41:16,239
[Lee]
The video that you just watched?

799
00:41:17,173 --> 00:41:18,708
This was what
Ysay and I were doing.

800
00:41:19,476 --> 00:41:21,911
I asked Ysay to help me write
you a song for our monthsary.

801
00:41:22,713 --> 00:41:23,914
Ysay told me
that you've been wanting me

802
00:41:24,047 --> 00:41:25,715
to write you a song
for the longest time.

803
00:41:29,253 --> 00:41:32,489
Why was Ysay afraid
I'd catch you?

804
00:41:33,657 --> 00:41:36,059
Because it was supposed to be
a surprise!

805
00:41:37,161 --> 00:41:38,661
It's true, Naih.

806
00:41:38,963 --> 00:41:40,264
Lee asked for my help.

807
00:41:40,396 --> 00:41:43,099
I just wanted to help because
I wanted to surprise you, too,

808
00:41:43,233 --> 00:41:44,668
but this happened.

809
00:41:45,135 --> 00:41:50,407
My God! Sorry.
Sorry, friend. Sorry, Ysay.

810
00:41:51,574 --> 00:41:56,547
Sorry. Sorry, Mine.
I'm just afraid of losing you.

811
00:41:56,981 --> 00:41:59,650
Our monthsary is still on,
right?

812
00:42:02,085 --> 00:42:04,054
Super sorry.

813
00:42:05,054 --> 00:42:09,425
Sorry, too, friend. Sorry.

814
00:42:09,559 --> 00:42:11,695
Mine, sorry!

815
00:42:13,097 --> 00:42:14,465
[Lorde]
No one's gonna say sorry to me?

816
00:42:14,931 --> 00:42:17,601
All your crazy girlfriend's
punches landed on me, Master!

817
00:42:18,601 --> 00:42:19,402
Ouch.

818
00:42:19,769 --> 00:42:21,271
My face, my poor face!

819
00:42:29,947 --> 00:42:32,682
[cafe music
playing over speaker]

820
00:42:33,449 --> 00:42:34,617
-[Deib sighs with relief]
-[Max] MOO!

821
00:42:35,251 --> 00:42:36,353
[Deib] Hi, Babybabe!

822
00:42:36,487 --> 00:42:39,523
Just finished
2 hours of school service.

823
00:42:40,724 --> 00:42:42,393
34 more hours to go.

824
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:45,362
What did Headmaster make you do?

825
00:42:45,795 --> 00:42:47,697
Clean all the boys' restrooms.

826
00:42:47,831 --> 00:42:49,233
Huh?

827
00:42:49,365 --> 00:42:51,168
But it's okay. I enjoyed it.
It's a different experience.

828
00:42:51,302 --> 00:42:54,771
Wow, Deib Lohr Enrile
cleaning the washroom!

829
00:42:54,905 --> 00:42:55,873
Right?

830
00:42:56,172 --> 00:42:57,641
What do you have to do tomorrow?

831
00:42:58,141 --> 00:42:59,443
Tomorrow...

832
00:43:00,277 --> 00:43:06,150
I asked Headmaster for a day off
since it's our monthsary.

833
00:43:06,717 --> 00:43:07,617
He said yes.

834
00:43:07,751 --> 00:43:09,052
That's nice, MOO.

835
00:43:09,552 --> 00:43:11,422
But I hope we can hang
with the whole gang

836
00:43:11,554 --> 00:43:14,657
before our romantic dinner
tomorrow.

837
00:43:14,791 --> 00:43:15,626
Yeah.

838
00:43:16,293 --> 00:43:19,496
Let's do something
to lessen Michiko's sadness.

839
00:43:20,130 --> 00:43:21,164
Yeah.

840
00:43:23,300 --> 00:43:25,603
I think I know what to do
with the gang tomorrow.

841
00:43:25,735 --> 00:43:26,670
What?

842
00:43:26,804 --> 00:43:30,106
Kurt from Southbay
has a new karaoke place...

843
00:43:31,041 --> 00:43:31,775
Wow!

844
00:43:31,909 --> 00:43:33,010
We should all come!

845
00:43:33,876 --> 00:43:38,282
I think it's a great time for us
to support Kurt and Michiko.

846
00:43:40,384 --> 00:43:42,186
Really? So you're friends
with Kurt now, huh?

847
00:43:42,686 --> 00:43:44,420
Of course!
Speaking of new friends!

848
00:43:44,922 --> 00:43:45,623
Jaybee!

849
00:43:45,755 --> 00:43:46,990
What's up?
Sorry, it was traffic.

850
00:43:47,123 --> 00:43:47,958
It's okay, bro.

851
00:43:48,092 --> 00:43:49,226
-[Jaybee] Sorry!
-[Deib] All good!

852
00:43:49,659 --> 00:43:50,260
Hi, guys!

853
00:43:50,827 --> 00:43:53,364
Jaybee, this is Max,
my girlfriend.

854
00:43:53,496 --> 00:43:53,864
Hi, Max!

855
00:43:53,998 --> 00:43:54,498
Hello!

856
00:43:54,632 --> 00:43:55,132
Michiko.

857
00:43:55,264 --> 00:43:56,532
Hi, Michiko.

858
00:43:59,335 --> 00:44:02,572
Max, thanks for reforming Deib!

859
00:44:04,273 --> 00:44:07,543
Thanks, Deib,
for tagging my bonsai shop

860
00:44:07,677 --> 00:44:09,246
in your IG post
with your brother.

861
00:44:09,713 --> 00:44:11,347
Got lots of orders from Benison.

862
00:44:11,481 --> 00:44:12,583
-[Deib] Really?
-[Jaybee] Yeah!

863
00:44:12,715 --> 00:44:14,018
Sure thing, bud!

864
00:44:14,150 --> 00:44:17,320
-Is this my other order?
-Yeah, here.

865
00:44:17,954 --> 00:44:18,655
How much do I owe you?

866
00:44:18,789 --> 00:44:20,224
It's on me!

867
00:44:20,356 --> 00:44:21,358
No, seriously, how much?

868
00:44:21,492 --> 00:44:23,527
I insist! It's my gift to you!

869
00:44:23,661 --> 00:44:24,494
Are you sure?

870
00:44:24,628 --> 00:44:25,728
Yeah!

871
00:44:25,862 --> 00:44:28,699
Tomorrow I'm throwing a party
at Kurt's videoke place.

872
00:44:29,065 --> 00:44:29,800
You should come!

873
00:44:29,932 --> 00:44:30,634
Sure!

874
00:44:30,768 --> 00:44:31,601
Bring Digz.

875
00:44:31,735 --> 00:44:32,168
Game!

876
00:44:32,302 --> 00:44:32,969
I'll see you there?

877
00:44:33,103 --> 00:44:33,603
Game!

878
00:44:33,737 --> 00:44:34,505
Alright, cool!

879
00:44:34,637 --> 00:44:36,606
I still can't believe
we're friends.

880
00:44:37,074 --> 00:44:38,742
You'll get used to it!

881
00:44:43,112 --> 00:44:45,983
[water running]

882
00:44:47,251 --> 00:44:47,851
[turns off faucet]

883
00:44:49,385 --> 00:44:50,420
[phone chimes]

884
00:44:58,896 --> 00:45:02,565
Tiago said you said no.
Think you can say no now?

885
00:45:03,833 --> 00:45:06,469
Maybe your niece needs to be
hospitalized again

886
00:45:06,603 --> 00:45:07,938
for you to say yes?

887
00:45:10,574 --> 00:45:16,480
[tense music playing]

888
00:45:23,086 --> 00:45:28,492
[Boyet] I'll do it.
Just leave my niece out of this.

889
00:45:35,498 --> 00:45:37,668
[tense music continues]

890
00:45:37,800 --> 00:45:39,402
-[door opens]
-Uncle Boyet!

891
00:45:41,938 --> 00:45:42,405
RJ!

892
00:45:42,539 --> 00:45:43,574
Where are you going?

893
00:45:49,813 --> 00:45:54,418
RJ, I just need
to take care of something.

894
00:45:55,385 --> 00:45:56,987
[Boyet]
Take care of everyone for me.

895
00:45:57,887 --> 00:46:02,326
Don't forget
mom's medicine schedule.

896
00:46:02,793 --> 00:46:05,929
And take care of Max, okay?

897
00:46:07,030 --> 00:46:10,534
Uncle Boyet,
why are you saying goodbye

898
00:46:10,666 --> 00:46:12,001
like you're never coming back?

899
00:46:12,869 --> 00:46:13,737
I have to go.

900
00:46:21,844 --> 00:46:28,684
[suspenseful music playing]

901
00:47:03,619 --> 00:47:05,621
[Tiago] If you don't go with us,

902
00:47:05,755 --> 00:47:08,192
Boss will come after you next.

903
00:47:08,826 --> 00:47:09,860
Lord, forgive me
for what I'm about to do.

904
00:47:09,992 --> 00:47:12,829
Max and I will go on a date
for our first month.

905
00:47:12,963 --> 00:47:15,599
I'd like to ask
for your permission, sir.

906
00:47:15,731 --> 00:47:17,266
For the girl who never fails
to make me laugh.

907
00:47:17,400 --> 00:47:19,036
-[friends squealing]
-[Lee] Naih...

908
00:47:19,536 --> 00:47:22,505
[Deib] Max,
can we reenact our first kiss?

909
00:47:22,639 --> 00:47:25,108
Reservation? I didn't make one.

910
00:47:25,242 --> 00:47:27,978
[receptionist] I think this is
a surprise from Mr. Yanai.

911
00:47:28,411 --> 00:47:29,045
Tob?

912
00:47:30,447 --> 00:47:31,815
[Michiko]
Thank you for coming back.
